{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"stroke-miterlimit","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-miterlimit","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p>如果两条线交汇在一起形成一个尖角，而且属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-linejoin\">stroke-linejoin</a></code>指定了<code>miter</code>，斜接有可能扩展到远远超过出路径轮廓线的线宽。属性<code>stroke-miterlimit 对斜接长度和</code><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-width\">stroke-width</a></code>的比率<code>强加了一个极限。当极限到达时，交汇处由斜接变成倒角。</code></p>\n\n<p>斜接长度（斜接的外尖角和内夹角之间的距离）与<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-width\">stroke-width</a></code>的比率，直接跟两条线之间的角度（θ）有关，用如下方程表示：</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">miterLength / stroke-width = 1 / sin ( theta / 2 )\n</pre>\n\n<p>举个例子，一个极限为 1.414 斜接，θ小于 90 度的把斜接会转换成倒角，一个极限为 4.0 的斜接，θ小于 29 度的斜接会转换成倒角，一个极限为 10.0 的斜接，θ小于大约 11.5 度的斜接会转换成倒角。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>外观属性</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td>&lt;miterlimit&gt; | inherit</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">初始值</th>\n   <td>4</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可动性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/painting.html#StrokeMiterlimitProperty\" rel=\" noopener\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"miterlimit\">&lt;miterlimit&gt;</dt>\n <dd>对斜角长度与<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-width\">stroke-width</a></code>的比率的限制。&lt;miterlimit&gt;的值必须是一个大于或等于 1 的<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#number\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Number\">&lt;number&gt;</a>。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用<code>stroke-miterlimit</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#shape\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#Shape\">形状元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Element#textcontent\" title=\"en/SVG/Element#TextContent\">文本内容元素</a>&nbsp;»</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"stroke-miterlimit","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"stroke-miterlimit","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"stroke-miterlimit","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stroke-miterlimit","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/stroke-miterlimit/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute","title":"SVG 属性参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/stroke-miterlimit","title":"stroke-miterlimit"}],"pageTitle":"stroke-miterlimit - SVG | MDN","noIndexing":false}}